flowchart TD
    A[User uploads one PDF or multiple images] --> B[FastAPI /upload saves files in uploads/]
    B --> C{Upload shape}
    C -->|Single PDF| D[Orchestrator process_upload_batch -> analyze_document]
    C -->|Single image| E[Orchestrator process_document -> analyze_images_from_folder]
    C -->|Multiple images| F[Orchestrator process_upload_batch -> analyze_images_from_folder]

    D --> G[PDF router chooses PyMuPDF or MarkItDown]
    G --> H[Each page rendered to image]
    E --> I[Image folder loader gathers images]
    F --> I
    I --> J[Optional Azure Document Intelligence on images]

    H --> K[LLM page structure analysis]
    J --> K
    K --> L[Smart chunking]
    L --> M[LLM visual element extraction]
    M --> N[Enriched chunk text built]
    N --> O[Azure OpenAI embeddings generated]
    O --> P[Chunks staged in ContextManager]
    P --> Q[Batch upload to Azure AI Search]

    R[User asks question via /ask] --> S{Question type}
    S -->|Understanding / engineering QA| T[Hybrid retrieval from Azure AI Search]
    S -->|Tables, charts, exports, calculations| U[Code Agent path]
    T --> V[gpt-5-pro answers with evidence and reasoning]
    U --> W[GPT-5 Code Agent returns tables / charts / files]
    V --> X[Answer returned to frontend]
    W --> X